headline: Countdown to Idexx (IDXX) Q3 Earnings: A Look at Estimates Beyond Revenue and EPS
summary: Besides Wall Street's top-and-bottom-line estimates for Idexx (IDXX), review projections for some of its key metrics to gain a deeper understanding of how the company might have fared during the quarter ended September 2025.
